lick &#8220;Update Plugins&#8221;.'=>'Järgmistele pluginatele on saadaval uuendusi.  Vali soovitavad ja klõpsa "Uuenda pluginad".','The following plugins were successfully updated:'=>'Järgnevad pluginad uuendati edukalt:','The following themes are installed but incomplete.'=>'Järgnevad teemad on paigaldatud, kuid mittetäielikud.','The following themes failed to update:'=>'Järgnevate teemade uuendamine ebaõnnestus:','The following themes have new versions available. Check the ones you want to update and then click &#8220;Update Themes&#8221;.'=>'Järgmistele teemadele on saadaval uuendusi.  Vali soovitavad ja klõpsa "Uuenda teemasid".','The following themes were successfully updated:'=>'Järgnevad teemad uuendati edukalt:','The following translations failed to update:'=>'Järgnevate tõlgete uuendamine ebaõnnestus:','The following translations were successfully updated:'=>'Järgnevad teemad uuendati edukalt:','The ftp PHP extension is not available'=>'PHP FTP-laiendust ei leitud','The grid view for the Media Library requires JavaScript. <a href="%s">Switch to the list view</a>.'=>'Meediateegi ikoonivaade vajab JavaScripti. <a href="%s">Lülitu nimistuvaatele</a>.','The installer attempted to contact a random hostname (%s) on your domain.'=>'Paigaldus üritas võtta ühendust suvalise hostiga (%s) selles domeenis.','The item you are trying to move to the Trash no longer exists.'=>'Elementi mida proovisid prügikasti saata ei ole enam olemas.','The item you are trying to restore from the Trash no longer exists.'=>'Elementi mida proovisid prügikastist taastada ei ole enam olemas.','The language pack is missing either the %1$s or %2$s files.'=>'Tõlkepakis puudub  %1$s või %2$s fail.','The left-hand navigation menu provides links to all of the WordPress administration screens, with submenu items displayed on hover. You can minimize this menu to a narrow icon strip by clicking on the Collapse Menu arrow at the bottom.'=>'Vasakul asuv menüü sisaldab viiteid kõigile WordPressi haldust